about.LicenseAgreement: Ngokusebenzisa le software, uvumelana nemibandela yesivumelwano selayisense yesoftware ye-Neuralium. Ungabuka inguqulo yakamuva yesivumelwano selayisense yesoftware ku-:

account.PleaseImportOrCreateWalletAccount: Sicela ungenise noma wakhe i-akhawunti yesikhwama

verifyAccount.Title: Ukuqinisekiswa kwe-Akhawunti
verifyAccount.IntroductionText: Ukuze uvikele ukuhlukumezeka, inqubo yokudala i-akhawunti kumele idlule ngendlela ethile yokuqinisekisa. Kuya ngokuthi ukuphi, izinketho ezahlukene ziyatholakala.
verifyAccount.ResultsSuccess: Ukuqinisekiswa kube yimpumelelo! i-ID yakho ye-akhawunti manje iqinisekisiwe ngocingo.
verifyAccount.ResultsFailure: Ukuqinisekiswa bekungokwehluleka. Ungazama futhi emahoreni angama-24.
verifyAccount.DefaultHelpText: Lapha kufanele ukhethe indlela yokuqinisekisa phakathi kwezinketho ezitholakalayo. Indlela ngayinye inezinzuzo zayo kanye nokuphazamiseka. Sicela ukhethe eyodwa efanele wena.
verifyAccount.TESTNETHelpText: Ku-TESTNET, ukuqinisekisa kungadluliswa ukuze kudalwe i-akhawunti ngokushesha.
verifyAccount.AppointmentsHelpText: Uzoqala inqubo yokuqinisekisa ukuqokwa kweNeuralium. Le nqubo ingahlala izinsuku eziningi futhi kuzofanele ube khona lapho uzoqokwa lapho usuku luqinisekisiwe. Izinzuzo: engaziwa.
verifyAccount.POWHelpText: Kuzofanele ukhiphe ubufakazi bokubiza umsebenzi obiza kakhulu we-CPU. Uma isiqediwe, i-akhawunti yakho izokwazi ukufaka engcupheni yethusi yokuqala neyesi-2 njengeServer.

appointments.Title: Ukuqinisekiswa kokuqokwa
appointments.IntroductionText: Ukuhamba komsebenzi wokuqokwa kwenzelwe ukuqinisekisa abasebenzisi abahlosiwe ngenkathi kugcinwa iningi lezikhukhula kulolu hlelo.
appointments.RequestAppointmentText: Ukuze uqale inqubo, sicela ucele ukubonana ngokuqokwa. Isicelo sokuqokwa sizokwenziwa futhi isiqinisekiso kufanele sitholwe esikhathini esizayo.
appointments.AppointmentConfirmedText: Isicelo sakho sokuqokwa sesiqinisekisiwe futhi usuku nesikhathi sokuqokwa sekusethiwe. Qiniseka ukuthi uzoba khona ngesikhathi!
appointments.AppointmentVerificationRequestedText: Isicelo sokuqinisekiswa kokuqokwa sesithunyelwe. Manje silindele ukuqinisekiswa.
appointments.InvalidPuzzleEngineVersion: Uhlobo lwenjini lwephazili olungalungile. Sicela uvuselele inguqulo yakho yesoftware.

puzzles.Title: Iphazili
puzzles.TimeBeforeAppointment: Iseshini yakho yepuzzle izokuqala maduze. Isikhathi esilinganiselwe esisele ngaphambi kokucela isikhathi sakho
puzzles.WaitingForPuzzle: isikhathi se-puzzle kufanele siqale noma yisiphi isikhathi manje. Njengamanje elindele imiyalo ye-puzzle ...
puzzles.CompletedAndSend: Iphazili yakho isiqediwe. Sicela ulinde ngenkathi imiphumela icutshungulwa.
puzzles.PreparingPackage: Sicela ulinde ngenkathi inqubo yokuqokwa iphothula futhi ithumela imiphumela yokuqinisekiswa.

sms.Title: Ukuqinisekiswa kwe-SMS
sms.ConfirmationCodeHint: Ikhodi yokuqinisekisa okungenzeka ukuthi uyitholile ngenqubo yokuqokwa.
sms.PhoneNumberHint: Inombolo yocingo lapho ungathola khona umyalezo we-SMS.
sms.IntroductionText: Lapha sizokuqinisekisa i-akhawunti yakho ngokusebenzisa inombolo yocingo evumelekile.
sms.InvalidChineseConfiguration: E-China, ngenxa yobulukhuni bokuthumela i-SMS, iKhodi yokuqinisekisa evumelekile kufanele itholakale kuqala.
sms.ResultsSuccess: Ukuqinisekiswa kube yimpumelelo! i-ID yakho ye-akhawunti manje iqinisekisiwe ngocingo.
sms.ResultsFailure: Ukuqinisekiswa bekungokwehluleka. Ungazama futhi emahoreni angama-24.

accountPublication.AccountPublicationProcessExplanation: Ngaphambi kokuthi noma yikuphi ukusebenza kwenziwe ku-blockchain, i-akhawunti yakho kufanele yethulwe esidlangalaleni kwabanye. I-akhawunti yakho izoqinisekiswa, futhi izolungela ukusebenza uma sekuqinisekisiwe ngebhlokhi.
accountPublication.AccountPublicationFailed: Kuvele iphutha ngenkathi kushicilelwa i-akhawunti. Ukushicilela kuhlulekile.
accountPublication.CanCloseWindow: Manje usungavala ngokuphepha leli windi ngenkathi ulindele ukuthi kufike ubufakazi.
accountPublication.NeedBlockchainSynced: IBlockchain idinga ukuvumelaniswa ukuze ishicilele i-akhawunti.
accountPublication.NeedPeerToPublish: Akunantanga eyanele exhunywe ukuze uqale ukushicilela i-akhawunti.

mining.ExplainInfoPanel: Izibalo ezahlukahlukene eziwusizo ze-adn mayelana nezikhathi zakho zezimayini
mining.Explain: Lapha ungabeka ikhompiyutha yakho ukuthi isebenze ngokuyenza yenze iphazili yezibalo ukuvula amaNeuralium amasha.
mining.Miningportalert: Qaphela: Ukuze ube ngowami, itheku lakho le-TCP kufanele lisebenze kwezinye izindawo eziku-p2p. Ukwabelana kuyindlela yokuziphatha efanelekile ku-p2p. Uma ufisa ukufaka umgodi emihlanganweni yesibili neyokuqala yezimayini, imbobo KUFANELE ixhunyaniswe ngaphandle kwalokho i-node ayisoze yakwazi ukuphumelela kunoma iyiphi ibhulokhi. Uyacelwa ukuthi uqinisekise ukuthi uvula i-firewall yakho futhi unike amandla ukudluliswa kwembobo.
mining.ConfirmClearCachedCredentials: Ngabe kufanele kuchazwe iziqinisekiso zokumbiwa phansi kwemayini? (lokhu kungathinta ukusebenza kabi futhi akunconywa)
mining.PortNotConnectableCantMine: Ukuze uzongifaka kuma tiers 1 noma 2nd, port yakho p2p kumele ixhumeke. Ayikwazi ukunika amandla izimayini njengoba zinjalo. Uma ungakwazi ukuvula imbobo, vele ulungiselele izimayini ukuze zisebenze kuhlaka lwesi-3.

send.NotesDescription: Inothi ongakukhetha elizogcinwa kumarekhodi akho siqu.

testMode.ParagrahOne: Okwamanje ukwimo ye-TESTNET. Uhlobo lwe-testnet lwenzelwe ukuhlolwa ngezinto ezintsha ezingahle zingasebenzi noma zingasebenzi njengoba bekuhlosiwe. Ungabika noma yiziphi izimbungulu, izinkinga noma iziphakamiso ongaba nazo ngezixazululo zethu ezinikezele.
testMode.ParagrahTwo: Kwindlela ye-TESTNET, noma yimaphi amathokheni we-neuralium atholakele enzelwe ukuhlolwa kuphela futhi angeke asetshenziswe kunethiwekhi yokukhiqiza ye 'MainNet'. Amathokheni atholwe kumodi ye-TESTNET nawo angalahleka noma asethe kabusha nganoma yisiphi isikhathi ngaphandle kwesaziso sangaphambilini.
testMode.Warning: I-node nesikhwama okwamanje kumodi yeTestNet kunethiwekhi ehlukile.
testMode.Period: Lokhu kwakhiwa kwe-TESTNET kusebenza kuze kube ngo-Agasti 18th 2020.

wallet.PleaseCreateOrCopy: Dala isikhwama esisha noma ulayishe esivele sikhona.
wallet.WalletWaitMessage: Manje sakha ama-akhawunti akho nezinkinobho zokuphepha. Lokhu kungathatha imizuzu eminingi. Ngiyabonga ngokubekezela kwakho.
wallet.Completed: Isikhwama sakho senziwe kahle. Manje njengesinyathelo esilandelayo, sincoma ngokuqinile ukuthi wenze isipele ngokuphepha sayo yonke ifolda yesikhwama. Sincoma kakhulu ukuthi ususe ngokomzimba ukhiye ophambili kufolda ye-akhawunti yakho futhi uyigcine ngokuphepha kudrayivu engaphandle kwekhompyutha yakho.
wallet.WalletPath: Ungathola isikhwama sakho esisha ngendlela elandelayo
